00:00:45.394 --> 00:00:47.640
- Welcome to a Conversation with History.

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:48.800
I'm Harry Kreisler of

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:51.650
the Institute of International Studies.

00:00:51.650 --> 00:00:54.840
Our guest today is Laura d'Andrea Tyson

00:00:54.840 --> 00:00:58.110
who is professor of business
administration and economics

00:00:58.110 --> 00:01:00.940
and director of the Institute for Business

00:01:00.940 --> 00:01:04.280
and Social Impact at the
Haas School of Business.

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:07.760
She is a former chairman of the
Council of Economic Advisors

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:10.230
in the Clinton administration.

00:01:10.230 --> 00:01:13.910
Laura served as dean of the Haas School

00:01:13.910 --> 00:01:16.050
and of the London Business School.

00:01:16.050 --> 00:01:21.050
Professor Tyson is the 2015
Harvest Distinguished Lecturer.

