Laura, I wanna thank you

00:57:33.070 --> 00:57:36.290
for taking the time to be on our program.

00:57:36.290 --> 00:57:40.240
And I wanna, again, recommend
to our audience that

00:57:40.240 --> 00:57:45.080
they watch your lecture as a
companion to this interview.

00:57:45.080 --> 00:57:47.093
And I think the two together will

00:57:47.093 --> 00:57:52.093
give an impressive sense of the ideas that

00:57:52.500 --> 00:57:54.780
you've carried throughout your life.

00:57:54.780 --> 00:57:56.446
Thank you.
